      "id": "PopularPost306454",
      "post_content": "Banding sucks, but THIS is how good Alpha Flavor is: I was Commenting on Every Card Today, when I hit Bad Moon. Seriously cool card :)   \n  \nThen I hit Bayou. And I was reminded of Scooby-Doo on Zombie Island. THEN I decided to songfic tribute to [Terror](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror) on Bayou. :P This completely derailed my Comment on Every Card project, as I was immediately desiring to go on YouTube and look up crossovers of that song with Everything Halloweeny. :P   \n  \nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67dVpgUry7Q  \n  \nthere is an Alvin and the Chipmunks version of this song, and I really, really want Magic to go BACK to Innistrad RIGHT. NAOW. And there needs to be a Mystery, Inc. reference. I want to go Trick-or-Treating. The Day Before Easter :P   \n  \n  \nAnd that is why [Bayou](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bayou) and [Bad Moon](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bad Moon) are the BEST CARDS in Alpha, Ever! XD",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost306454\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_post\">Banding sucks, but THIS is how good Alpha Flavor is: I was Commenting on Every Card Today, when I hit Bad Moon. Seriously cool card :) <br/><br/>Then I hit Bayou. And I was reminded of Scooby-Doo on Zombie Island. THEN I decided to songfic tribute to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Terror\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Terror\">Terror</a> on Bayou. :P This completely derailed my Comment on Every Card project, as I was immediately desiring to go on YouTube and look up crossovers of that song with Everything Halloweeny. :P <br/><br/>http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=67dVpgUry7Q<br/><br/>there is an Alvin and the Chipmunks version of this song, and I really, really want Magic to go BACK to Innistrad RIGHT. NAOW. And there needs to be a Mystery, Inc. reference. I want to go Trick-or-Treating. The Day Before Easter :P <br/><br/><br/>And that is why <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bayou\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bayou\">Bayou</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Bad Moon\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Bad Moon\">Bad Moon</a> are the BEST CARDS in Alpha, Ever! XD</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl07_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '306454'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Pos